snippet.textDisplay:
As an avid enjoyer of red dead redemption 2, I think it would be a great idea if you did a playthrough of the main + side story missions because if you havnt completed them already you're missing out on the best parts of the game. 

Theres also a red dead redemption online mode that has roles which are basically jobs. Theres one called the trapper and its centered all around hunting and delivering animal pelts and whatnot. But you should complete the main story before touching online

Also that 3 star male moose you killed is the rarest animal in the game. I've played close to 200 hours in the game and still havnt found one yet, congratulations üòÖ
snippet.textOriginal:
